# GET /api/files — list tracked saves

### list files returns 200 with array
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files
Accept: application/json

{%
  test('status 200', () => {
    expect(response.status).toBe(200);
  });
  test('body is array', () => {
    expect(Array.isArray(response.parsedBody)).toBe(true);
  });
%}

### POST on /api/files is rejected
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files

